title: Delays after crash on M62 motorway
text:
Highways England @HighwaysYORKS Follow #West_Yorkshire On the #M62 e/bound at J28, the earlier accident has been cleared and the closed lane re-opened. Queues beginning to ease.
08:45 - 10 Sep 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite Highways England @HighwaysYORKS Follow #West_Yorkshire On the #M62 e/bound at J28, we're helping @ wyp_rpu at the accident scene. Still one lane closed. It's slow on the approach
08:39 - 10 Sep 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite Highways England @HighwaysNEAST Follow #West_Yorkshire One lane closed on the #M62 e/bound at J28 due to an accident. Expect delays. Queues back to J27. http://t.co/JFxLAxbhkC
